    public class ObjectComboBoxTableCell<S,T>
extends ObjectTableCell<S,T>
    Represent an editable cell in a TableView that update its content when a property is modified and allow changes with a ComboBox. A lot of its content is based ojn ComboBoxTableCell

    Created by Thomas Couchoud (MrCraftCod - zerderr@gmail.com) on 28/05/2017.

    Since:
    2017-05-28
    Author:
    Thomas Couchoud
